               CHANGES in 1.3

o  Changed colors to make them easier to read with a gray background.

o  Added a real template file suitable for printing.

o  Added an anonymous FTP netrc file and howto instructions.

o  Reorganized and simplified the function key bindings.

o  Added column number display in addition to line number display.

o  Added the split horizontal and vertical window feature.

o  Added and mouse cut and paste feature.




